npm install -g @angular/cli [installs the CLI for angular --  g for globally] 

ng new public

navigate to Angular App:
   -ng build --watch
   -ng g s http

create new component;
   -ng generate component [component_nam]

Injecting Service [Navigate to Angular App]:
   - ng g s http
   - Register = app.module.ts [providers]
   - Httpclient = app.module.ts [imports]
   
